### QA2 — FUNCTIONAL TEST
### Event Passport PWA — Template
### Tests the full attendee flow: register → scan → qualify → admin view.
### Run QA1 first to confirm the API is reachable.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# CONFIGURATION
# Update these variables before running.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@eventId = <your-event-id>

# Get this from the Admin panel → Sponsors → QR Code value
@qrCodeSponsor = <sponsor-qr-code-uuid>

# Staff credentials — create via POST /api/auth/staff/register first
@staffEmail = staff@yourevent.example.com
@staffPassword = <your-staff-password>

# After running F01, paste the returned token here for F02–F05
@attendeeToken = <paste-token-from-F01-here>

# After running F06, paste the returned access_token here for F07
@staffToken = <paste-access-token-from-F06-here>

# Production example:
# @baseUrl = https://your-app.up.railway.app/api


# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# F01 — Register with valid data
# Expected: 201 + token
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
### F01
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "QA Test User",
  "email": "qa.functional.test@example.com",
  "company": "QA Labs",
  "rgpdConsent": true,
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# F02 — Resume session with valid token
# Expected: 200 + attendee data
# NOTE: paste token from F01 into @attendeeToken above
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
### F02
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/resume?token={{attendeeToken}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# F03 — Check passport after registration
# Expected: 200 + 0 stamps
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
### F03
GET {{baseUrl}}/stamps/passport?token={{attendeeToken}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# F04 — Scan valid QR code
# Expected: 201 + stamp registered
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
### F04
POST {{baseUrl}}/stamps/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{attendeeToken}}",
  "qrCode": "{{qrCodeSponsor}}"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# F05 — Check passport after scan
# Expected: 200 + 1 stamp
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
### F05
GET {{baseUrl}}/stamps/passport?token={{attendeeToken}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# F06 — Staff login with correct credentials
# Expected: 200 + access_token
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
### F06
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/staff/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{staffEmail}}",
  "password": "{{staffPassword}}"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# F07 — Admin dashboard after registration
# Expected: 200 + updated stats
# NOTE: paste access_token from F06 into @staffToken above
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
### F07
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard?eventId={{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}
